Package: pleior
Title: Pleiotropy analysis in genome-wide association studies (GWAS)
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Dany", "Mukesha", , "danymukesha@gmail.com", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-9514-751X"))
Description: Systematically identify and interpret pleiotropic genetic variants 
    (SNPs associated with multiple traits) using GWAS data, with a focus 
    on understanding shared biological mechanisms.
